{"tid":2264646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[慎入多圖]6歲女童臉長巨大血管瘤面容扭曲　媽媽鼓勵愛女妝扮影靚相重拾自信","createTime":"2020-10-30T20:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T10:21:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f4def41e2e5067c563d2d86dd163f577fd4f2b8b","tid":2264646,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:35:49.000Z","msg":"巴西一名女童面上長有先天性血管瘤，自一出世腫瘤已伴著著她，雖然未有嚴重影響健康，卻令她外貌奇特與別不同。小女孩的自我形象低落，甚至不想拍照及照鏡，媽媽見狀，為愛女打扮化妝，讓她穿上漂亮的衣飾，並拍照上載至網絡，令女兒重拾自信，展示獨特的美。<br />\n<br />\n長血管瘤致面容扭曲<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報道，巴西6歲女孩Vitoria患有先天性血管瘤，一邊面自出世時已長有腫瘤，影響面頰之外，更有一邊鼻子及嘴巴受影響而歪掉，面容扭曲。不幸中大幸是，血管瘤不影響Vitoria日常生活，亦不會帶來疼痛，只需要大約每隔數月定期進行檢查及治療，而日常玩耍時，宜小心避免弄傷血管瘤就可。<br />\n<br />\n面上長有巨大血管瘤，令Vitoria的自我形象日漸低落，備受歧視，一外出就飽受他人奇異目光，令她沒有自信心。她有一位4歲妹妹，36歲媽媽Rose表示大女曾很羨慕沒有患病的妹妹︰<br />\n&quot;大女曾經不想拍照及照鏡子，總是說想長得跟妹妹一樣，不想要血管瘤。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n從打扮影靚相獲自信<br />\n媽媽知道女兒其實很貪靚，便為她配搭不同服裝、改變妝髮，開始為她拍照，Vitoria享受其中，更因而獲得信心。而爸媽於去年11月為女兒開設Instagram，分享她的時尚百變造型照片。<br />\n<br />\nVitoria的經歷及照片大獲網民讚好，現時有3萬6千名網民追蹤其IG。可是，有些網民認為父母利用女兒的殘疾去斂財，媽媽受訪表示被誤解，一度覺崩潰，絕望到想關閉女兒的IG帳號。所幸有大量網民鼓勵她，並支持Vitoria繼續展示獨特美麗的一面，分享正能量，展示患病者同樣可以活出漂亮。<br />\n<br />\nVitoria現正嘗試新的治療方法，以減少血管瘤內的血液量，從而令腫瘤不會惡化及變大，家人希望女兒將來可進行去切除腫瘤的手術，不用備受歧視。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/tumour_thumb_20201030_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2Ftumour_thumb_20201030_ch_1024.jpg&h=63ac72ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/p22_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2Fp22_1024.jpg&h=439cf38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/p21_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2Fp21_1024.jpg&h=fe569f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/p12_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2Fp12_1024.jpg&h=3ffdd655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/p23_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2Fp23_1024.jpg&h=9e0a2a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/p16_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2Fp16_1024.jpg&h=ff44bcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2790000/2790316/P11_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2790000%2F2790316%2FP11_1024.jpg&h=0af28405&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee64faf73497f0eeb8b8af5a082cf83ad17d3ceb","tid":2264646,"uid":246648,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:47:56.000Z","msg":"其實都真係幾靚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680274de2895c47de28bad1f440a657e9c6531af","tid":2264646,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fc178e8abc97e17460a97456bf96f01ac284e22","tid":2264646,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:51:28.000Z","msg":"拜登表示可以"},{"pid":"ea281770c75aa997b53d662b9868181478dd925e","tid":2264646,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:58:16.000Z","msg":"想屌"},{"pid":"eb257bb97f84b7f72cf